2/http://www.ambafrance-uk.org/Declaration-by-the-Franco-German%2C4519.html |archivedate=2014-03-27 |deadurl=yes }}}}{{refTag|1={{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/04/world/europe/04iht-poll.4.11666423.html | title = The leader of Europe? Answers an ocean apart | author = Freed, John C. | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2008-04-04 | accessdate = 2011-03-28 | archive-date = 2017-06-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170628215610/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/04/world/europe/04iht-poll.4.11666423.html | dead-url = no }}}}。

