德國採行[[社会市场经济|社会市场经济]]<ref group="書">{{harvnb|賴麗琇|1994|p=181}}</ref><ref group="書">{{harvnb|肖捷|1992|p=1}}</ref>，工業基礎堅固，擁有高技術的勞工、龐大[[股票|股本]]，较低的腐败程度{{refTag|1={{cite web |url=http://archive.transparency.org/policy_research/surveys_indices/cpi/2009/cpi_2009_table |title=CPI 2009 table |publisher=Transparency International |accessdate=2012-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511052011/http://archive.transparency.org/policy_research/surveys_indices/cpi/2009/cpi_2009_table |archivedate=2012-05-11 }}}}，及高創新能力{{refTag|1={{cite web |url=http://www.bcg.com/documents/file15445.pdf |title=The Innovation Imperative in Manufacturing: How the United States Can Restore Its Edge |date=March 2009 |accessdate=2011-03-19 |publisher=Boston Consulting Group |archive-date=2011-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520154532/http://www.bcg.com/documents/file15445.pdf |dead-url=no }}}}。德国为[[各国出口额列表|世界第三大出口国]]{{refTag|name="auto1"}}及欧洲第一大经济体；按國際匯率計算，為[[各国国内生产总值列表_(国际汇率)|世界第4大經濟體]]{{refTag|name=wbpdf|1={{cite web |url=http://siteresources.worldbank.org/DATASTATISTICS/Resources/GDP.pdf |work=The World Bank: World Development Indicators database |title=Gross domestic product (2009) |date=2010-09-27 |publisher=World Bank |accessdate=2011-01-01 |archive-date=2009-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090912122439/http://siteresources.worldbank.org/DATASTATISTICS/Resources/GDP.pdf |dead-url=no }}<br />[https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/fields/2195.html Field listing – GDP (official exchange rate)]}}，以[[购买力平价|购买力平价]]計算則為[[各国国内生产总值列表_(购买力平价)|世界第5大經濟體]]{{refTag|name=WBWDI|1={{cite web |url=http://siteresources.worldbank.org/DATASTATISTICS/Resources/GDP_PPP.pdf |work=The World Bank: World Development Indicators database |title=Gross domestic product (2009) |date=2010-09-27 |publisher=World Bank |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-date=2014-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209081011/http://siteresources.worldbank.org/DATASTATISTICS/Resources/GDP_PPP.pdf |dead-url=no }}<br />
[https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2001rank.html Field listing – GDP (PPP exchange rate)]}}。

[[第三产业|服务业]]（包括[[通訊技术|通訊产业]]）对德国国内生产总值的贡献达到71%，工业和农业则分别贡献28%和1%{{refTag|name="CIA"}}。根据[[欧洲统计局|欧洲统计局]]2015年1月数据，德国失业率为4.7%，为28个欧盟成员国中最低{{refTag|name="Eurostat"|1={{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/documents/2995521/6664116/3-02032015-AP-EN.pdf/28d48055-3894-492d-a952-005097600ee0|title=Eurostat: Euro area unemployment rate at 11.2%|publisher=eurostat|date=2015-03-02|accessdate=2017-11-23|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010085610/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/documents/2995521/6664116/3-02032015-AP-EN.pdf/28d48055-3894-492d-a952-005097600ee0|dead-url=no}}}}；其青年失业率为7.1%，亦为欧盟最低{{refTag|name="Eurostat"}}。根据[[经济合作与发展组织|经济合作与发展组织]]报告，德国为世界上劳动生产率最高的国家之一{{refTag|1={{cite web|title=Labour productivity levels in the total economy|url=http://stats.oecd.org/Index.aspx?DatasetCode=LEVEL|publisher=OECD|accessdate=2014-12-12|archive-date=2014-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210125946/http://stats.oecd.org/Index.aspx?DatasetCode=LEVEL|dead-url=no}}}}。

