===人口===
{{main|德國人口|德意志人}}
[[File:Population_of_German_territories_1800_-_2000.JPG|thumb]]
根据2011年人口普查数据，德国人口约为8,020万{{refTag|name="File 2013"|1=[https://www.destatis.de/DE/PresseService/Presse/Pressekonferenzen/2013/Zensus2011/bevoelkerung_zensus2011.pdf?__blob=publicationFile ''Zensus 2011: Bevölkerung am 9. Mai 2011'']. 2013-06-01}}，而至2015年6月30日这一数字上升至8,150万{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=https://www.destatis.de/EN/FactsFigures/SocietyState/Population/CurrentPopulation/Tables/Census_SexAndCitizenship.html|title=Population based on the 2011 Census - German Statistical Office ("Destatis")|work=destatis.de|accessdate=2016-01-13|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628112855/https://www.destatis.de/EN/FactsFigures/SocietyState/Population/CurrentPopulation/Tables/Census_SexAndCitizenship.html|dead-url=no}}}}，到2015年12月31日至少达到8,190万{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=https://www.destatis.de/EN/PressServices/Press/pr/2016/01/PE16_032_12411.html|title=Significant population growth to at least 81.9 million in 2015 - German Statistical Office ("Destatis")|work=destatis.de|accessdate=2016-03-21|archive-date=2016-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416132733/https://www.destatis.de/EN/PressServices/Press/pr/2016/01/PE16_032_12411.html|dead-url=no}}}}。德国为欧盟人口最多的国家，在欧洲则为第2位（居[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]之后），[[国家人口列表|世界第16位]]{{refTag|1={{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2119rank.html?countryName=Lebanon&countryCode=le&regionCode=me&rank=126 |title=Country Comparison :: Population |publisher=CIA |accessdate=2011-06-26 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106143620/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2119rank.html?countryName=Lebanon&countryCode=le&regionCode=me&rank=126 |dead-url=no }}}}。其[[国家人口密度列表|人口密度]]为227人/平方千米（588人/平方英里）。总[[各国人口预期寿命列表|预期寿命]]为80.19岁（男性77.93岁；女性82.58岁）{{refTag|name="CIA"}}。[[总和生育率|总和生育率]]为每名妇女生育1.41名子女（2011年估计），即年增长率约千分之8.33，为[[各国生育率列表|世界最低之一]]{{refTag|name="CIA"}}。自1970年代起，德国的[[死亡率|死亡率]]持续高于其[[生育率|生育率]]{{refTag|1={{cite web | title = Demographic Transition Model | publisher = Barcelona Field Studies Centre | date = 2009-09-27 | url = http://geographyfieldwork.com/DemographicTransition.htm | accessdate = 2011-03-28 | archive-date = 2010-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100527180111/http://geographyfieldwork.com/DemographicTransition.htm | dead-url = no }}}}，但自2010年代以来其生育率和移民率有一定提升{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=http://www.thelocal.de/society/20101229-32091.html#.UXUZKEpTv3N|title=Birth rate on the rise in Germany|work=The Local|accessdate=2014-09-28|archive-date=2013-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925054451/http://www.thelocal.de/society/20101229-32091.html#.UXUZKEpTv3N|dead-url=no}}}}，受优良教育的移民数量尤有提升{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/elite-young-immigrants-could-provide-future-stability-for-german-economy-a-885647.html|title=The New Guest Workers: A German Dream for Crisis Refugees|date=2013-02-28|work=Spiegel Online|accessdate=2014-09-28|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129042506/http://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/elite-young-immigrants-could-provide-future-stability-for-german-economy-a-885647.html|dead-url=no}}}}{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=http://www.dw.de/more-skilled-immigrants-find-work-in-germany/a-16696339|title=More skilled immigrants find work in Germany|work=Deutsche Welle|accessdate=2014-09-28|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129134223/http://www.dw.de/more-skilled-immigrants-find-work-in-germany/a-16696339|dead-url=no}}}}。

四个颇具规模的族群因其祖先在相应区域长期定居，被称为“国家少数民族”{{refTag|name="BMI 2010"|1={{cite web |date=May 2010 |title=National Minorities in Germany |url=http://www.bmi.bund.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/EN/Broschueren/2010/nat_minderheiten.pdf?__blob=publicationFile |format=PDF |others= |publisher=[[德國聯邦內政部|Federal Ministry of the Interior (Germany)]] |pages= |id=Article number: BMI10010 |accessdate=2014-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421151141/http://www.bmi.bund.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/EN/Broschueren/2010/nat_minderheiten.pdf?__blob=publicationFile |archivedate=2013-04-21 }}}}。在北端的[[石勒苏益格-荷尔斯泰因|石勒苏益格-荷尔斯泰因]]-{zh-hans:州; zh-hant:邦}-有近50,000名[[丹麦人|丹麦裔]]{{refTag|name="BMI 2010"}}；在[[萨克森自由州|萨克森]]和[[勃兰登堡|勃兰登堡]]的[[卢萨蒂亚|卢萨蒂亚]]地区有近60,000名[[斯拉夫人|斯拉夫裔]][[索布人|索布人]]；[[罗姆人|罗姆人]]和[[辛提人|辛提人]]生活于联邦全境；[[弗里斯兰人|弗里斯兰人]]则生活于石勒苏益格-荷尔斯泰因西岸及[[下萨克森|下萨克森]]西北部{{refTag|name="BMI 2010"}}。近500万德国人生活在海外{{refTag|1=Auswärtiges Amt Berlin, [http://www.konsularinfo.diplo.de/Vertretung/konsularinfo/de/06/Wahl/Wahlneu.html Konsular Info] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306214813/http://www.konsularinfo.diplo.de/Vertretung/konsularinfo/de/06/Wahl/Wahlneu.html |date=2012-03-06 }}. Auswärtiges Amt, Berlin. Accessed 17 June 2015.}}。

=== 移民 ===
[[File:COB_data_Germany.PNG|thumb]]
2014年，德国8,100万居民中有近700万无德国国籍，其中96%生活在德国西部，大多数居于城市区域内{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=http://www.dw.de/german-population-rises-thanks-to-immigration/a-16525083|title=German population rises thanks to immigration|work=Deutsche Welle|accessdate=2014-09-28|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129134220/http://www.dw.de/german-population-rises-thanks-to-immigration/a-16525083|dead-url=no}}}}{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=https://www.destatis.de/DE/Publikationen/Thematisch/Bevoelkerung/MigrationIntegration/Migrationshintergrund2010220107004.pdf|title=Population and employment: Population with migrant background – Results of the 2010 microcensus|date=2012-03-13|publisher=|accessdate=2014-09-28|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707151903/https://www.destatis.de/DE/Publikationen/Thematisch/Bevoelkerung/MigrationIntegration/Migrationshintergrund2010220107004.pdf|dead-url=no}}}}。

1960年代和1970年代，德国政府邀请“{{le|客籍工人|Gastarbeiter}}”移居德国。许多企业在这些工人完成培训后将其留在德国国内继续工作，由此德国的移民人口稳固提升{{refTag|name="File 2013"}}。截至2011年，近600万外国公民（占总人口7.7%）在德国注册登记{{refTag|name="File 2013"}}。

[[德国联邦统计局|德国联邦统计局]]将其公民根据移民背景分类。2009年，全国20%居民（超过1,600万人）具有移民或部分移民背景（包括被遣返的[[德意志人|德意志裔]]）{{refTag|1={{Cite news | title=20% of Germans have immigrant roots | newspaper=Burlington Free Press | page= 4A | date=2010-07-15 }}}}。2010年，在拥有18岁以下子女的家庭中，29%至少父母有一方具有移民背景{{refTag|name="destatis.de"|1={{cite web |url=https://www.destatis.de/EN/Publications/STATmagazin/Population/2012_03/2012_03MigrantBackground.html |title=Publikation — STATmagazin — Population — Families with a migrant background: traditional values count — Federal Statistical Office (Destatis) |publisher=Destatis.de |date=2012-03-13 |accessdate=2012-11-04 |archive-date=2012-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114171259/https://www.destatis.de/EN/Publications/STATmagazin/Population/2012_03/2012_03MigrantBackground.html |dead-url=no }}}}。

2015年，{{le|联合国经济和社会事务部|United Nations Department of Economic and Social Affairs}}人口分部统计德国共有1,200万国际移民，约占全球2.44亿移民的5%，居世界第二位{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/en/development/desa/population/migration/publications/migrationreport/docs/MigrationReport2015_Highlights.pdf|title=International Migration Report 2015 - Highlights|publisher=United Nations Department of Economic and Social Affairs|date=2015|accessdate=2016-06-09|archive-date=2016-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513001608/http://www.un.org/en/development/desa/population/migration/publications/migrationreport/docs/MigrationReport2015_Highlights.pdf|dead-url=no}}}}。在移民占总人口数量百分比方面，德国位居欧盟第7位，世界第37位。截至2014年，最大的移民族群来自土耳其（2,859,000），其次为波兰（1,617,000）、俄罗斯（1,188,000）和意大利（764,000）{{refTag|1={{cite web |url=http://www.destatis.de/DE/ZahlenFakten/GesellschaftStaat/Bevoelkerung/MigrationIntegration/Migrationshintergrund/Tabellen/MigrationshintergrundStaatsangehoerigkeit.html |title=Bevölkerung nach Migrationshintergrund |publisher=destatis |date=2014 |accessdate=2016-06-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714155444/https://www.destatis.de/DE/ZahlenFakten/GesellschaftStaat/Bevoelkerung/MigrationIntegration/Migrationshintergrund/Tabellen/MigrationshintergrundStaatsangehoerigkeit.html |archivedate=2016-07-14 }}}}。自1987年来，近300万德意志人（多数来自前[[东方集团|东方集团]]国家领土）行使其回归权移居德国{{refTag|1={{cite web|url=http://www.migrationpolicy.org/article/fewer-ethnic-germans-immigrating-ancestral-homeland/|title=Fewer Ethnic Germans Immigrating to Ancestral Homeland|publisher=Migration Information Source|date=February 2004|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811005859/http://www.migrationpolicy.org/article/fewer-ethnic-germans-immigrating-ancestral-homeland/|dead-url=no}}}}。

